menu "CNN Inference"

config CNN_MODEL_PARTITION
    bool "Load model from flash partition instead of rodata"
    default n
    help
        When enabled, the .espdl model is loaded from a dedicated OTA-style
        flash partition labelled "model" rather than being linked as rodata.
        Use this if you want to update the model over-the-air without
        reflashing the entire firmware.

        When disabled (default), the model binary is embedded directly into
        the firmware image via EMBED_FILES and loaded from flash rodata.

endmenu
